HOLLYWOOD LÆRER Å SNAKKE

454
00:46:18.040 --> 00:46:20.840
GULLGRUVE
FOR TALEPEDAGOGER


455
00:46:26.140 --> 00:46:31.940
Altså: Ta-te-ti-to-tu.

456
00:46:37.940 --> 00:46:42.440
Nei, nei, Miss Lamont!
Rrrunde toner! Rrrunde toner!


457
00:46:42.940 --> 00:46:46.640
La meg få høre replikken din.

458
00:46:46.840 --> 00:46:52.340
-"Jeg kan'ke usstå ham."
-Jeg kan ikke uuuuutstå ham.


459
00:46:56.240 --> 00:46:59.040
-Kan.
-"Kæn."


460
00:47:00.040 --> 00:47:04.340
-Kaaan.
-"Kæææn."


461
00:47:07.440 --> 00:47:12.040
Glimrende.
"Rundt i ring de raske rytterne red."


462
00:47:13.640 --> 00:47:16.440
Nei, rring.

463
00:47:16.640 --> 00:47:20.940
"Rundt i ring de raske rytterne red."

464
00:47:21.340 --> 00:47:24.240
-Skal jeg fortsette?
-Ikke ta notis av meg.


465
00:47:24.540 --> 00:47:30.140
"Syndige Cæsar satt i stolen
