men mor pranger ikke om perlepris.


471
00:47:54.540 --> 00:47:59.640
Hun prøver hans prektige perler,
men pruter aldri om prisen."


472
00:48:00.040 --> 00:48:02.540
Praktfullt! Gi oss en til!

473
00:48:03.140 --> 00:48:06.040
"Moses får skoser,
for Moses' roser-


474
00:48:06.440 --> 00:48:09.140
